<subSubSection id="7D025EF41A0FB56D88F405DFC650AB6C" pageId="720" pageNumber="721" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="1EB863168B7F99E6849CB77C8F272952" pageId="720" pageNumber="721">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BA9A7A542DF58CA4A7742A2F46FA32CE" pageId="720" pageNumber="721">
The range of this species extends from southern Quebec (Serge Laplante pers. comm. 2002) to southeastern South Dakota (Kirk and Balsbaugh 1975: 30), south to 
<normalizedToken id="EFD69C2F0D2D3D8FBBC3003606E74246" originalValue="“Texas”">&quot;Texas&quot;</normalizedToken>
(Lindroth 1968: 819) and central South Carolina (Ciegler 2000: 105).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
